    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs super smoothly, looks sharp, and has been really well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
