    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a recently serviced variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The double-VANOS system is quiet and responsive, ensuring a flat torque curve. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, the suspension bushings are tight, and the cooling system has been overhauled to maintain thermal efficiency during spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
