    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 530i in Alpine White with a Black Dakota Leather interior. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning buyer looking for luxury without the showroom price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular highway commuting. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather seats are supple with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the iDrive navigation, heated seats, and premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust, having received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake service. The Continental tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. This is a reliable, high-performing sedan that has been treated with respect by its previous owner. Full service records are available for your review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for those seeking both reliability and sophisticated performance. This automobile has undergone a rigorous professional inspection, confirming its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. The interior remains refined, and the exterior retains its distinguished character, reflecting a history of diligent care. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances everyday utility with an elevated driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
