    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in solid mechanical condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Maintenance is current, including a recent VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under load. The chassis is sharpened with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the communicative, balanced handling characteristics this platform is known for. It pulls strong and clean to the 8,000 RPM redline with a linear torque curve. A well-sorted enthusiast spec ready for the road.",
